		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Pottsville</placeName> <date>July 14&#47;64</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><del>Dear</del> Honorable Sir&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">It is a long time since I<lb/> wrote to you.  But <del>it was</del> not negligence on<lb/> my part <del>but rather</del> is to blame&#44; but rather<lb/> these upsetting times.  I am happy&#44; to find in<lb/> your paper that you are still grinding<add>&#63;</add> with<lb/> a strong hand the shop Jewish religious conditions<lb/> in <placeName>America</placeName>.  God bless you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">As far as I and my family are<lb/> concerned&#58; Everything is fine.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Let me tell you something about<lb/> our own congregation because I know you<lb/> are interested in religious things.  Our congr.<lb/> got many new members in the last year and<lb/> a new life came into the meetings.  A regular <add><date>Rosh Hodesh</date> <add>&#63;</add> <date>Sabbath</date></add> service is held each <add>Hebrew</add> and other holidays.<lb/>  I can flatter myself that everybody is<lb/> satisfied with my service and I&#39;ll try to<lb/> keep it up.  My speeches on the holidays<lb/> caused large attendances of various<lb/> denominations.  Last <add>Hebrew</add> <add><date>Shabu&#45;oth</date></add> for the first</p>
				<p rend="Note&#58;">&#8220;<date>Rosh Hodesh</date> <add>&#63;</add> <date>Sabbath</date>&#8221; in the paragraph above is inserted in the left margin.</p>
			<pb n="2R"/>
				<p rend="align(center)">2</p>
				<p>time I confirmed 4 children and everybody<lb/> was highly<add>&#63;</add> pleased.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The 8 synagogue was filled by people<lb/> of various denominations.  Many people thanked<lb/> me and <add>I got generous presents from</add> the parents of the children whom I had<lb/> confirmed.  I hope to be able to give you soon<lb/> good news again.</p>
				<p>&#40;Please&#44; read English on 3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> page of original&#41;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Another point I wish to mention<lb/> Since I came to <placeName>Pottsville</placeName> I was two<lb/> times in <placeName>Danville</placeName> as a <add>Hebrew</add> <add>preacher</add> I<lb/> found this congregation in a very bad con&#45;<lb/>dition.  It is a herd without a leader.<lb/>  The dust in the synagogue was &#189; inch high<lb/> because it has not been used for a long<lb/> while.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Let me tell you an incident<lb/> concerning <persName>Mr. Oettinger</persName> of the <placeName>Danville</placeName><lb/> Parnass.  On <date>Sunday July 3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi></date> he was<lb/> arrested at the meeting of the congregation<lb/> was put in jail and brought to <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> the next day.  I <sic>dont</sic> doubt that you</p>
